5705521473%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ex2\"\n        title=\"ex2\"\n        src=\"/static/af247029e14d8f36cafb23e3d2e08adb/38772/ex2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/af247029e14d8f36cafb23e3d2e08adb/d2f63/ex2.jpg 163w,\n/static/af247029e14d8f36cafb23e3d2e08adb/c989d/ex2.jpg 325w,\n/static/af247029e14d8f36cafb23e3d2e08adb/38772/ex2.jpg 606w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 606px) 100vw, 606px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Layout 작업이 사라지고, Recalculate Style – Composite Layer 작업만 존재한다.</p>\n<p>모바일에서 두 예제를 확인해 보면, 두번째 예제가 첫번째 예제보다도 빠르고 매끄럽게 이동하는 것을 확인할 수 있다.\n브라우저의 특성을 이해하면 간단한 속성 변경만으로도 많은 성능향상을 할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"참조-문서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EC%A1%B0-%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"참조 문서 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참조 문서</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/speed/layers/\">http://www.html5rocks.com/en/tutorials/speed/layers/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://speakerdeck.com/jaffathecake/rendering-without-lumps\">https://speakerdeck.com/jaffathecake/rendering-without-lumps</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.chrisdanford.com/blog/2011/07/24/understanding-hardware-compositing-css-transforms/\">http://